										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-2610" src="http://clockworktwist.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/cute-puppy-cupcake-dog-love-jack-russel-teriier-happy-super-excited-epic-lolcat.jpg" alt="" width="557" height="409" srcset="https://clockworktwist.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/cute-puppy-cupcake-dog-love-jack-russel-teriier-happy-super-excited-epic-lolcat.jpg 557w, https://clockworktwist.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/cute-puppy-cupcake-dog-love-jack-russel-teriier-happy-super-excited-epic-lolcat-300x220.jpg 300w" sizes="(max-width: 557px) 100vw, 557px" /></p>
<p>It&#8217;s almost time for cake!  And ice creme!  And Twist!!  I&#8217;m so excited right now.  You don&#8217;t even know.  But first and foremost, the last of the free preview chapters is up today!</p>
<h4 style="text-align: center;"><a href="/book-three-dreamer/dreamer-chapter-3/">Click right here to read the third chapter of Dreamer!</a></h4>
<p>Did you miss the first chapter?  <a href="http://clockworktwist.com/book-three-dreamer/dreamer-chapter-1/" target="_blank">Click right here </a>to read it before moving on.</p>
<p>And yes, the Kindle version and all other eBook versions are now available for pre-order!  Click the logo of your choice to pre-order your copy now.</p>
<p><center><br />
<a href="http://www.amazon.com/Clockwork-Twist-Dreamer-Emily-Thompson-ebook/dp/B00P1JG9LY" target="_blank"><img decoding="async" class="alignnone" src="http://i1.wp.com/media.corporate-ir.net/media_files/irol/17/176060/KindleLogos/Kindlelogo/scr2555-proj697-a-kindle-logo-rgb-lg.jpg?resize=148%2C40" alt="" width="148" height="40" /></a> <a href="http://www.smashwords.com/books/view/488847" target="_blank"><img decoding="async" class="alignnone" src="https://dwtr67e3ikfml.cloudfront.net/static/1/swlogo.png" alt="" width="160" height="43" /></a></center></p>
<h4 style="text-align: center;">The book will be available tomorrow!!</h4>
<p>Oh, what a thrill!  I can&#8217;t wait for all of you to see what happens next.  As I&#8217;ve said before, this is one of my favorite books in the series.  I hope that you enjoy it just as much as I do.  And thanks as always for all of the wonderful support!  You guys are the best.</p>
<p>And don’t forget!  There’s still time to enter to win a free copy of Dreamer!  <a title="!!Fan art and photo contest!!" href="http://clockworktwist.com/blog/2014/10/19/fan-art-and-photo-contest/" target="_blank">Click here for details</a>.</p>
